member.name: TfAnchor
member.summary: Elements of the TfAnchor enumeration specify the start anchor or end anchor of an object.

member.name: TfAnchor.TF_ANCHOR_START
member.summary: Specifies the start anchor of the ITfRange object.

member.name: TfAnchor.TF_ANCHOR_END
member.summary: Specifies the end anchor of the ITfRange object.
